perative CT findings of Sapien and CoreValve transcatheter heart valves. <em>RadioGraphics</em> 2014;34(6):1517–1536.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.346130149">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25310415/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Transcatheter+aortic+valve+replacement%3A+postoperative+CT+findings+of+Sapien+and+CoreValve+transcatheter+heart+valves&amp;author=RA+Salgado&amp;author=RPJ+Budde&amp;author=T+Leiner&amp;publication_year=2014&amp;journal=RadioGraphics&amp;pages=1517-1536&amp;doi=10.1148%2Frg.346130149&amp;pmid=25310415">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">11.</div><div id="r11" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Salgado RA, Leipsic JA, Shivalkar B, et al. Preprocedural CT evaluation of transcatheter aortic valve replacement: what the radiologist needs to know. <em>RadioGraphics</em> 2014;34(6):1491–1514.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.346125076">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25310413/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Preprocedural+CT+evaluation+of+transcatheter+aortic+valve+replacement%3A+what+the+radiologist+needs+to+know&amp;author=RA+Salgado&amp;author=JA+Leipsic&amp;author=B+Shivalkar&amp;publication_year=2014&amp;journal=RadioGraphics&amp;pages=1491-1514&amp;doi=10.1148%2Frg.346125076&amp;pmid=25310413">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">12.</div><div id="r12" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Tchetche D, Dumonteil N, Sauguet A, e